#: ../../user_interface/menu/view_menu/audio_spectrum.rst:13
msgid "Audio Spectrum"
msgstr "Ljudspektrum"

#: ../../user_interface/menu/view_menu/audio_spectrum.rst:18
msgid "Contents"
msgstr "Innehåll"

#: ../../user_interface/menu/view_menu/audio_spectrum.rst:20
msgid ""
"This allows you to monitor the audio properties of your clip in detail. The "
"graph only display data while the clip is playing in the clip or project "
"monitor."
msgstr ""
"Gör det möjligt att detaljerat övervaka klippets ljudegenskaper. Diagrammet "
"visar bara data medan klippet spelas på klipp- eller projektskärmen."

#: ../../user_interface/menu/view_menu/audio_spectrum.rst:23
msgid ""
"It graphs the loudness of the audio (in decibels - vertical axis) for each "
"audio frequency (horizontal axis) in the current frame. The blue curve is +- "
"the maximum over the previous few samples."
msgstr ""
"Diagrammet visar ljudets styrka (i decibel på den vertikala axeln) för varje "
"ljudfrekvens (horisontella axeln) i den nuvarande bildrutan. Den blåa kurvan "
"är +- maximum över några av de tidigare samplingarna."

#: ../../user_interface/menu/view_menu/audio_spectrum.rst:26
msgid ""
"See also :ref:`spectrogram` scope which displays a graphical representation "
"of the audio spectrum over the entire clip."
msgstr ""
"Se också oscilloskopet :ref:`spectrogram` som visar en grafisk "
"representation av hela klippets ljudspektrum."

#: ../../user_interface/menu/view_menu/audio_spectrum.rst:34
msgid ""
"For more information see `Granjow's blog <http://kdenlive.org/users/granjow/"
"introducing-scopes-audio-spectrum-and-spectrogram>`_ on Audio Spectrum"
msgstr ""
"För mer information se `Granjow's blog <http://kdenlive.org/users/granjow/"
"introducing-scopes-audio-spectrum-and-spectrogram>`_ om ljudspektrum"
